<div class="text-center py-16">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Find the perfect time for your event</h1>
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    Create an event, share it with friends, and find out when everyone is available.
    No account required.
  </p>
  <%= link_to "Create an Event", new_event_path, class: "inline-block bg-indigo-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors text-lg no-underline" %>
</div>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-8">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 text-center">
    <div class="text-3xl mb-3">&#128221;</div>
    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">1. Create</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Set up your event with possible dates, times, and questions for your group.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 text-center">
    <div class="text-3xl mb-3">&#128279;</div>
    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">2. Share</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Send the link to your friends. No sign-up needed for them to respond.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 text-center">
    <div class="text-3xl mb-3">&#9989;</div>
    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">3. Decide</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">See everyone's availability at a glance and pick the best time.</p>
  </div>
</div>
